ous.\r\n\r\nI also do not see an obvious \"degrees of freedom\" problem here, e.g., why the MLE would be singular.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alkaline-ml/pmdarima/issues/492/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alkaline-ml/pmdarima/issues/492/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sktime/sktime/issues/comments/1086273632","html_url":"https://github.com/sktime/sktime/issues/1871#issuecomment-1086273632","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sktime/sktime/issues/1871","id":1086273632,"node_id":"IC_kwDOCVKAsc5Avzhg","user":{"login":"fkiraly","id":7985502,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc5ODU1MDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7985502?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly","html_url":"https://github.com/fkiraly","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fkiraly/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-04-01T19:59:06Z","updated_at":"2022-04-01T19:59:06Z","author_association":"COLLABORATOR","body":"Opened an issue on `pmdarima` here: https://github.com/alkaline-ml/pmdarima/issues/492","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sktime/sktime/issues/comments/1086273632/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hoo